To create image:
	(TTY1) Run 0.... script 
	(TTY2) Run 1.... script in another tty 
	(TTY1) Run /tmp/_setup_docker.sh 
	(TTY2) Run 3.... script
TODO: It should be done with "docker build" command, but there were troubles. 

To run server:
Run 4.... script

To clean up:
Run 5.... script

Notice that server should be listed in /etc/hosts 
echo "127.0.1.1	www.example.com" > /etc/hosts